Balu  Balakrishnan 
Executive Compensation
As President and Chief Executive Officer at POWER INTEGRATIONS INC, Balu  Balakrishnan  made $3,810,373 in total compensation.  Of this total $557,462 was received as a salary, $10,000 was received as a bonus, $0 was received in stock options, $3,233,135 was awarded as stock and $9,776 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


